<p>For instance, is the following XSL, called with the following XML, what is the value of 'param'?</p>  <p>The issue is that I need to test for unmatched attributes, and it is apparently not an empty string.</p>  <pre><code>&lt;el&gt;&lt;/el&gt;&lt;!-- has no attribute 'attr' to match --&gt;  &lt;xsl:template match="*"&gt;    &lt;xsl:call-template name="template"&gt;         &lt;xsl:with-param name="param" select="@attr" /&gt;     &lt;/xsl:call-template&gt; &lt;/xsl:template&gt;   &lt;xsl:template name="template"&gt;     &lt;xsl:param name="param" /&gt;     &lt;xsl:value-of select="$param" /&gt; &lt;/xsl:template&gt; </code></pre>